flowchart TD
    A([Status change trigger]) --> B1[Single edit:\nVulnEditPanel → handleEditSave]
    A --> B2[Bulk action:\nVulnTable → handleBulkStatusChange]

    subgraph Duplicate CVE Detection Path
        DC1[User types CVE ID in VulnForm] --> DC2{onBlur / onChange /\nlookup / submit}
        DC2 --> DC3[findDuplicateCve\ncase-insensitive match against\nin-memory vulnerabilities]
        DC3 --> DC4{Match found?}
        DC4 -- No --> DC5[Continue normally]
        DC4 -- Yes, inline --> DC6[Show amber inline warning\nstatus · tier · assigned user\nView existing record link]
        DC4 -- Yes, on submit --> DC7[isDuplicateClosed\ncheck CLOSED_STATUSES]
        DC7 --> DC8{isClosed?}
        DC8 -- No: Active record --> DC9[DuplicateCveModal\nCancel · Submit Anyway]
        DC9 -- Cancel --> DC10[Close modal]
        DC9 -- Submit Anyway --> DC11[proceedWithSubmit\ncreate duplicate record]
        DC8 -- Yes: Closed record --> DC12[DuplicateCveModal\nReopen Existing ·\nSubmit as New · Cancel]
        DC12 -- Cancel --> DC10
        DC12 -- Submit as New --> DC11
        DC12 -- Reopen Existing --> DC13[handleReopenExisting\nchangeVulnerabilityStatus\nid · Risk Re-opened · no comment]
        DC13 --> DC14[Form reset\nonReopenSuccess callback\nRe-fetch vulns from PB]
    end

    B1 --> E1[scoreVulnerability updated fields\nwith current weights + thresholds]
    E1 --> E2[updateVulnerability → PocketBase\nWrite audit log: action=update]
    E2 --> E3{Status changed OR\nstatusComment present?}
    E3 -- No --> E8
    E3 -- Yes --> E4[changeVulnerabilityStatus\nvulnId · newStatus · comment · userId · orgId]

    B2 --> F1[Promise.allSettled:\nchangeVulnerabilityStatus for each id\nbulkAction=true]

    E4 --> G[pb.getOne current record\nrequestKey: null]
    F1 --> G

    G --> H{newStatus in CLOSED_STATUSES?\nRemediated · Accepted Risk\nFalse Positive · Risk Re-opened}
    H -- Yes isClosed --> I[updates: status · latestComment\nassigned_to = currentUserId]
    H -- No isClosed --> J[updates: status · latestComment\nassigned_to unchanged]
    I --> K[pb.update vulnerability]
    J --> K
    K --> L[Write audit log:\naction=status_change\npreviousStatus · newStatus · comment]
    L --> E8

    E8[Update vulnerabilities in local state] --> E9{newStatus === Remediated?}
    E9 -- Yes --> E10[triggerCatAnimation\nat mouse position]
    E9 -- No --> E11
    E10 --> E11

    F1 --> F2[Count succeeded / failed]
    F2 --> F3[Re-fetch all vulnerabilities from PB\nRe-score + update state]
    F3 --> F4[Clear selectedVulnIds]
    F4 --> F5{Any Remediated?}
    F5 -- Yes --> F6[triggerCatAnimation\ncenter of viewport]
    F5 -- No --> F7[Show bulk result banner:\nsucceeded · failed counts]
    F6 --> F7
    E11 --> F7
